Package com.samju.hospital.service

Interface PatientService

All Known Implementing Classes:
PatientServiceImpl
public interface PatientService
The PatientService interface defines the contract for managing Patient entities in the hospital management system.

Methods in this interface include:

  • createPatientRecord(Patient): Create a new patient record.
  • findByRegistration(String): Find a patient by their registration number.
  • findAllPatient(): Retrieve a list of all patients.

Usage example: 

 
 public class SomeController {
     PatientService patientService;

     // Some method that uses the service
     void someMethod() {
         Patient newPatient = // Create a new patient instance
         Patient createdPatient = patientService.createPatientRecord(newPatient);
         // Perform operations with the created patient record
     }
 }
